{"tid":202200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人成日買你唔想要既野比你 應該點做","createTime":"2017-04-15T10:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T16:51:21.000Z","uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95a4d5a8992650a6ae8d7f1843e49292fa867dba","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"屋企人成日冇啦啦買衫啊袋啊鞋等等比我<br />\n但佢地既taste同我永遠都好大出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺就好似將件印住大口仔既t-shirt比個廿幾數既人著<br />\n我明白佢地咁做係愛我<br />\n但佢地買既野根本唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又唔想浪費，好多都得個擺字<br />\n叫左勁多次話唔洗曬錢買野比我、我寧願佢地草返啲錢自己用，<br />\n結果下次又話買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要佢地次次買之前都唔問左我先，係買左先同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心唔想浪費，應該點做"},{"pid":"790bde5aa27385c8fd191514a67962376cea9a59","tid":202200,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"下次再買就開聲屌柒佢"},{"pid":"6cf6eae8ab8db5c47adb3820ebb663099e63413c","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次再買就開聲屌柒佢</blockquote><br />\n唔想咁直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次送野我話唔岩我 已經有d唔開心咁既款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6042e063a15914d0731836696e5e1d71d06b661","tid":202200,"uid":47620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"送俾人"},{"pid":"f8136f16e6dd961befa37072bf929301db2c8b38","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送俾人</blockquote><br />\n冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有時送既野都幾貴，冇啦啦送貴野比人好似唔知點咁"},{"pid":"29557e24f71183f971020e543e14d8c5c1329eb9","tid":202200,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"買番俾佢地"},{"pid":"0b607780b620dcd601fd840b5e1d32cd4ec2ba2e","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買番俾佢地</blockquote><br />\n佢地都係會照買野比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw不嬲間唔中會送野比屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef62ec716ae9d40e923caed52e2ab2edc33765c4","tid":202200,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"屋企著"},{"pid":"84208d9318446544846bb413bbf2bea641b6bebc","tid":202200,"uid":48585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"同佢地講 你再買嘅話聽日就燒返比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3761a7c0cd9e7c15dc0352d98f376a53f860c41f","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢地講 你再買嘅話聽日就燒返比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔捨得燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實唔係唔靚 但真係唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd181b003e1a6e66c955937a6ee83a4778e8fd21","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企著</blockquote><br />\n鞋啊袋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3313d7b1660982bb0b6145bd1355014f269ab798","tid":202200,"uid":95998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780aedcf387d8d482870d8e1840b3f131a0b01e1","tid":202200,"uid":25088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:51:2